parent1.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with shimmering feathers in the style of abstract art. It bursts into view above the crashing waves of an ancient shoreline at sunset, scattering glowing cinders from its tail amidst an environment of crumbling ruins and bioluminescent flora.

offspring.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with shimmering feathers in the style of expressionist art. It hovers in mid-air above a tranquil lagoon surrounded by towering ancient trees at dawn, trailing sparks of golden fire from its wings amidst an environment of moss-covered statues and bioluminescent mushrooms.
